description:
Entire 4 bedrooms apartment at first floor with 2 new bathrooms . Fully equipped kitchen, new marble counter top, dishwasher .

Bus #15 and # 17 in the front of the building which also connects you to the redline Fields Corner or Seven Hills Station. Only 2 miles to UMass Boston; 3 miles to North Eastern University.

The space
Kitchen ; 2 bathrooms;
Laundry in the building lower level. Coins operated.

Guest access
Basement laundry room .

Other things to note
There are bicycles you can borrow crossing the street in the front of St. Peter’s church.
